text: Lisa Read (born 26 August 1973) is an Australian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Australia Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in gymnastics Category:Commonwealth Games silver medallists for Australia
